## 4. المخطط المعماري (Architecture Flow)

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% NGFW Modules (Anomaly Sources)
    WAAP(WAAP Module: Initial Suspicion) --> |API Anomaly| UDE((Unified Causal Deception Engine))
    UBA(UBA Module: Out-of-role Action) --> |Behavior Anomaly| UDE
    IPS(IDS/IPS: Port Probe) --> |Network Anomaly| UDE
    DLP(DLP: Egress Match) --> |Data Match| UDE

    %% Trap Generation Phase
    UDE --> |Contextual Trap| TrapGen{Trap Generator}
    TrapGen --> |BOLA / Hidden API| W_Trap[WAAP Trap]
    TrapGen --> |Fake File / SQL Credentials| U_Trap[UBA Trap]
    TrapGen --> |Fake Banner / Tarpit| I_Trap[IDS Trap]
    TrapGen --> |Watermarked PII| D_Trap[DLP Trap]

    %% Injection and Action
    W_Trap --> Inject(Inject into target's normal flow)
    U_Trap --> Inject
    I_Trap --> Inject
    D_Trap --> Inject

    Inject --> Client[Target Actor]
    Client --> |Interacts with Trap| Engine_Verify[Engine: Causal Verification]

    Engine_Verify --> |Intent Proven 100%| Execute[Immediate Cross-Module Quarantine / Tarpit]
```

